# Per-replicate run byproducts: each rep-*/ holds a fresh workspace with a NESTED git repo plus the
# exported trail (runner-side/ + sut-authored/). Regenerable; kept out of version control to avoid
# nested-repo noise. The aggregated evidence (replicates.jsonl, aggregate.json) and the summary
